{"type":"message","id":"9c3e758d","parentId":"38b878ee","timestamp":"2026-03-10T06:11:10.352Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"太好了！成功获取了 tenant_access_token。现在我可以调用飞书日历 API 了。\n\n让我先获取当前用户的日历，然后测试创建事件。","thinkingSignature":"60af252b232540f7d13c78dcc3b47c349c21bd7a796478e43efd6b23e91657d8"},{"type":"text","text":"成功获取 API 凭证！现在让我测试一下日历功能，先获取你的日历 ID：\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_od9l5r44llmh_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"node -e \"const https = require('https'); const token = 't-g1043adWQP6WIP2BGH24G6K4IH35ANUH4F6C6SOO'; const req = https.request({hostname: 'open.feishu.cn', port: 443, path: '/open-apis/calendar/v4/calendars', method: 'GET', headers: {'Authorization': 'Bearer ' + token}}, res => {let d=''; res.on('data',c=>d+=c); res.on('end',()=>console.log(d));}); req.end();\""}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-cn","model":"MiniMax-M2.5","usage":{"input":18672,"output":200,"cacheRead":16705,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":35577,"cost":{"input":0.0056016,"output":0.00023999999999999998,"cacheRead":0.0005011499999999999,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.006342749999999999}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1773123064745}}
