{"type":"message","id":"5c0fb322","parentId":"20163a04","timestamp":"2026-03-10T06:11:38.202Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"找到了主日历 ID：feishu.cn_gYVN5ip57g1DCyK0GYM5xd@group.calendar.feishu.cn\n\n现在我有了完整的飞书日历 API 能力。但是当前工具箱里没有现成的日历工具。我需要创建一个技能，使用 exec 调用 API 的方式来管理日历。\n\n不过更好的方式可能是让 OpenClaw 支持飞书日历工具。让我告诉 Roger 目前的状况：\n- 凭证有效\n- 日历 API 可以调用\n- 但需要为这个日历功能写一个更完整的技能\n\n或者，我可以现在就用 API 创建测试事件，证明功能可用。\n\n让我先创建测试事件：","thinkingSignature":"ce055fc465f6e14c09cd4ec20086d992628f4e65663b464d48f5c809aa99e4ac"},{"type":"text","text":"找到了你的日历！让我创建一个测试事件：\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_89ugyrjwmwut_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"node -e \"\nconst https = require('https');\nconst token = 't-g1043adWQP6WIP2BGH24G6K4IH35ANUH4F6C6SOO';\nconst calendarId = 'feishu.cn_gYVN5ip57g1DCyK0GYM5xd@group.calendar.feishu.cn';\nconst startTime = Math.floor(Date.now()/1000);\nconst endTime = startTime + 3600;\nconst data = JSON.stringify({\n  calendar_id: calendarId,\n  event: {\n    summary: '测试会议 - 来自飞书日历技能',\n    description: '这是一条测试消息',\n    start: {timestamp: startTime, timezone: 'Asia/Shanghai'},\n    end: {timestamp: endTime, timezone: 'Asia/Shanghai'}\n  }\n});\nconst req = https.request({\n  hostname: 'open.feishu.cn',\n  port: 443,\n  path: '/open-apis/calendar/v4/calendars/' + calendarId + '/events',\n  method: 'POST',\n  headers: {'Authorization': 'Bearer ' + token, 'Content-Type': 'application/json', 'Content-Length': data.length}\n}, res => {let d=''; res.on('data',c=>d+=c); res.on('end',()=>console.log(d));});\nreq.write(data);\nreq.end();\n\""}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-cn","model":"MiniMax-M2.5","usage":{"input":19003,"output":458,"cacheRead":16705,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":36166,"cost":{"input":0.0057009,"output":0.0005496,"cacheRead":0.0005011499999999999,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.00675165}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1773123071556}}
