{"type":"message","id":"e20b03c8","parentId":"13e6c355","timestamp":"2026-03-10T06:18:57.654Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"看起来 v4 版本可能路径不同。让我查一下正确的 API 端点。可能需要用户授权才能访问日历。\n\n实际上，根据飞书文档，应用的 tenant_access_token 通常需要用户授权才能访问用户的日历数据。需要通过 OAuth 获取用户 token。\n\n但是这可能太复杂了。让我告诉用户这个情况，并建议使用 user_access_token 或者换一种方式。或者，让我尝试使用 Bitable 方案代替，因为那个已经验证可以工作了。\n\n让我先和用户说明情况。","thinkingSignature":"dbe32d464926eaa64110267c176fe3bf65f582f354f86135074367f805ac86d4"},{"type":"text","text":"遇到了权限问题。飞书日历 API 需要**用户授权**（user_access_token）才能访问个人日历，tenant_access_token 不够。\n\n---\n\n**有两个解决方案：**\n\n### 方案 A：用户授权（推荐）\n需要你在飞书开放平台开启\"用户授权\"功能，然后通过 OAuth 获取你的用户 token。\n\n### 方案 B：回到 Bitable 方案\n之前创建的 Bitable 日历已经可用，可以直接在飞书表格里看到事件，也可以在飞书文档/表格里查看。\n\n---\n\n**我的建议：** 方案 B 更简单可靠。你之前创建的 Bitable 表格已经可以正常使用了，功能一样。\n\n你想用哪个方案？"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-cn","model":"MiniMax-M2.5","usage":{"input":23264,"output":231,"cacheRead":16705,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":40200,"cost":{"input":0.0069792,"output":0.00027719999999999996,"cacheRead":0.0005011499999999999,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.007757549999999999}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1773123528670}}
{"type":"message","id":"60fa2f0b","parentId":"e20b03c8","timestamp":"2026-03-10T06:21:17.382Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Conversation info (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"message_id\": \"om_x100b55cfcb0ec0a0c499ac1e264c9fd\",\n  \"sender_id\": \"ou_19e8795f6cdecd6c5b87f1545d48b3ca\",\n  \"sender\": \"Roger\",\n  \"timestamp\": \"Tue 2026-03-10 14:21 GMT+8\"\n}\n```\n\nSender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"Roger (ou_19e8795f6cdecd6c5b87f1545d48b3ca)\",\n  \"id\": \"ou_19e8795f6cdecd6c5b87f1545d48b3ca\",\n  \"name\": \"Roger\"\n}\n```\n\n[message_id: om_x100b55cfcb0ec0a0c499ac1e264c9fd]\nRoger: 我还是选择方案A，告诉我开\"启用户授权\"功能怎么操作？"}],"timestamp":1773123677373}}
{"type":"message","id":"8ce92b7b","parentId":"60fa2f0b","timestamp":"2026-03-10T06:21:28.081Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Roger 选择方案 A，需要我告诉他如何开启用户授权功能。让我详细说明操作步骤。","thinkingSignature":"214528a2b8fa4e6289e4440c9209cad72e7bfd41443b55d2021aae874c28ee28"},{"type":"text","text":"好的！以下是开启用户授权的步骤：\n\n---\n\n### 操作步骤\n\n1. **打开飞书开放平台**\n   https://open.feishu.cn/\n\n2. **进入你的应用** → `cli_a920608cfff8dbb6`\n\n3. **开启用户授权**\n   - 左侧菜单 → **凭证与权限** → **用户授权**（或 \"OAuth 2.0\"）\n   - 开启以下权限：\n     - `calendar:calendar.event:create`\n     - `calendar:calendar.event:read`\n     - `calendar:calendar.event:update`\n     - `calendar:calendar.event:delete`\n\n4. **配置重定向URL（可选）**\n   - 在\"重定向URL\"添加：`http://localhost/oauth/callback`\n\n5. **发布新版本**\n   - 回到\"版本管理与发布\" → 发布新版本\n\n---\n\n开启后告诉我，我会生成一个授权链接让你点击，获取你的用户 token 后就可以在飞书日历里创建事件了！"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-cn","model":"MiniMax-M2.5","usage":{"input":36,"output":231,"cacheRead":16705,"cacheWrite":23287,"totalTokens":40259,"cost":{"input":0.0000108,"output":0.00027719999999999996,"cacheRead":0.0005011499999999999,"cacheWrite":0.0027944399999999996,"total":0.0035835899999999993}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1773123677381}}
{"type":"message","id":"a986bd96","parentId":"8ce92b7b","timestamp":"2026-03-10T06:23:58.614Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Conversation info (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"message_id\": \"om_x100b55cfc11cc4a0c4d82e184964e3f\",\n  \"sender_id\": \"ou_19e8795f6cdecd6c5b87f1545d48b3ca\",\n  \"sender\": \"Roger\",\n  \"timestamp\": \"Tue 2026-03-10 14:23 GMT+8\"\n}\n```\n\nSender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"Roger (ou_19e8795f6cdecd6c5b87f1545d48b3ca)\",\n  \"id\": \"ou_19e8795f6cdecd6c5b87f1545d48b3ca\",\n  \"name\": \"Roger\"\n}\n```\n\n[message_id: om_x100b55cfc11cc4a0c4d82e184964e3f]\nRoger: cli_a920608cfff8dbb6是哪个飞书应用？"}],"timestamp":1773123838609}}
