{"type":"message","id":"bb3ca82f","parentId":"8eda398d","timestamp":"2026-03-10T06:30:31.514Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Roger 已经开启了用户授权，现在他在问我是否被加入到访问控制列表（ACL）中。\n\n在飞书日历中，需要在日历的 ACL（访问控制列表）中添加应用或用户，才能让应用访问该日历。\n\n让我检查一下当前的日历 ACL 设置，看看是否有权限访问。但首先需要获取用户授权才能操作 ACL。\n\n让我先检查一下当前的权限状态。","thinkingSignature":"23c5da4027fbd5551cbd686b60786c91e2d8c1b4145ef63d4a79a1020e300f05"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_lp5plxh7gllm_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"node -e \"\nconst https = require('https');\nconst token = 't-g1043adWQP6WIP2BGH24G6K4IH35ANUH4F6C6SOO';\nconst calendarId = 'feishu.cn_gYVN5ip57g1DCyK0GYM5xd@group.calendar.feishu.cn';\n// 检查日历 ACL\nconst req = https.request({\n  hostname: 'open.feishu.cn',\n  port: 443,\n  path: '/open-apis/calendar/v4/calendars/' + calendarId + '/acl',\n  method: 'GET',\n  headers: {'Authorization': 'Bearer ' + token}\n}, res => {let d=''; res.on('data',c=>d+=c); res.on('end',()=>console.log(d));});\nreq.end();\n\""}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-cn","model":"MiniMax-M2.5","usage":{"input":36,"output":279,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":41379,"totalTokens":41694,"cost":{"input":0.0000108,"output":0.0003348,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0.0049654799999999995,"total":0.005311079999999999}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1773124223226}}
