{"type":"message","id":"2c603b44","parentId":"7991ffd8","timestamp":"2026-03-10T06:30:37.847Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"ACL API 不可用（404）。这可能是因为 tenant_access_token 没有权限访问日历 ACL。\n\n让我用 v3 版本试试，或者检查用户授权是否真的开启了。\n\nRoger 问的是我（应用）是否被加入到 ACL 中。这需要在日历设置里手动添加。\n\n让我直接告诉 Roger：需要在飞书日历的 ACL 中添加应用或用户的访问权限。","thinkingSignature":"2d4ac6d2b1825c18ecf0ad1978a458323b225c33fd3819d57400641b49813e53"},{"type":"text","text":"你需要在**飞书日历的 ACL（访问控制列表）**中添加我的访问权限：\n\n---\n\n### 操作步骤\n\n1. **打开飞书日历**\n   https://calendar.feishu.cn/\n\n2. **进入日历设置**\n   - 点击左上角**日历名称** → **日历设置**\n\n3. **添加访问权限**\n   - 在\"权限设置\"中添加：\n     - 你的应用 (`cli_a920608cfff8dbb6`) 或\n     - 你自己 (你的飞书账号)\n\n4. **或者直接分享日历链接**\n   - 生成邀请链接，把应用添加为\"可查看\"或\"可编辑\"\n\n---\n\n**完成后告诉我**，我会重新测试！"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-cn","model":"MiniMax-M2.5","usage":{"input":25009,"output":221,"cacheRead":16705,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":41935,"cost":{"input":0.007502699999999999,"output":0.0002652,"cacheRead":0.0005011499999999999,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.00826905}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1773124231816}}
{"type":"message","id":"d805a940","parentId":"2c603b44","timestamp":"2026-03-10T06:40:20.607Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Conversation info (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"message_id\": \"om_x100b55cf83fc08b0c4efb7c5df95bdf\",\n  \"sender_id\": \"ou_19e8795f6cdecd6c5b87f1545d48b3ca\",\n  \"sender\": \"Roger\",\n  \"timestamp\": \"Tue 2026-03-10 14:40 GMT+8\"\n}\n```\n\nSender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"Roger (ou_19e8795f6cdecd6c5b87f1545d48b3ca)\",\n  \"id\": \"ou_19e8795f6cdecd6c5b87f1545d48b3ca\",\n  \"name\": \"Roger\"\n}\n```\n\n[message_id: om_x100b55cf83fc08b0c4efb7c5df95bdf]\nRoger: 重新测试"}],"timestamp":1773124820601}}
{"type":"message","id":"592e9788","parentId":"d805a940","timestamp":"2026-03-10T06:40:46.658Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Roger says to test again. Let me try creating an event again.","thinkingSignature":"a737c4bae0efed41647fda047f0b0cfaa269f15a48bab69996c1305c13997a72"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_okuliz88nol6_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"node -e \"\nconst https = require('https');\nconst data = JSON.stringify({app_id: 'cli_a920608cfff8dbb6', app_secret: 'mUMS6FE8xIsudTUAvOk0cc2mHwjKxaLY'}); \nconst req = https.request({hostname: 'open.feishu.cn', port: 443, path: '/open-apis/auth/v3/tenant_access_token/internal', method: 'POST', headers: {'Content-Type': 'application/json', 'Content-Length': data.length}}, res => {let d=''; res.on('data',c=>d+=c); res.on('end',()=>{\n  const token = JSON.parse(d).tenant_access_token;\n  const calendarId = 'feishu.cn_gYVN5ip57g1DCyK0GYM5xd@group.calendar.feishu.cn';\n  // 尝试创建事件\n  const startTime = new Date(Date.now() + 3600000).toISOString();\n  const endTime = new Date(Date.now() + 7200000).toISOString();\n  const eventData = JSON.stringify({\n    event: {\n      summary: '测试会议',\n      start: {date_time: startTime, time_zone: 'Asia/Shanghai'},\n      end: {date_time: endTime, time_zone: 'Asia/Shanghai'}\n    }\n  });\n  const req2 = https.request({hostname: 'open.feishu.cn', port: 443, path: '/open-apis/calendar/v4/calendars/' + calendarId + '/events', method: 'POST', headers: {'Authorization': 'Bearer ' + token, 'Content-Type': 'application/json', 'Content-Length': eventData.length}}, res2 => {let d2=''; res2.on('data',c=>d2+=c); res2.on('end',()=>console.log(d2));});\n  req2.write(eventData);\n  req2.end();\n});}); \nreq.write(data); \nreq.end();\n\""}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-cn","model":"MiniMax-M2.5","usage":{"input":36,"output":470,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":41968,"totalTokens":42474,"cost":{"input":0.0000108,"output":0.0005639999