{"type":"message","id":"f7bd2cef","parentId":"0da405ff","timestamp":"2026-03-10T06:41:10.271Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Still failing. The issue is that the tenant_access_token doesn't have permission to access user calendars. We need user authorization (user_access_token) instead.\n\nLet me try to get the user authorization URL for Roger to click on. This requires the app to have the correct OAuth scopes configured.","thinkingSignature":"128936f1d9d567e459ebf4e33c263ee021691e34b95b0db5ef5872dc8ea45070"},{"type":"text","text":"仍然是 Bad Request。问题是 **tenant_access_token 无法访问个人日历**，需要你通过 OAuth 授权获取你的 **user_access_token**。\n\n---\n\n**现在需要你点击授权链接：**\n\n请打开以下链接进行授权：\n\n```\nhttps://open.feishu.cn/open-apis/connect/qrconnect?app_id=cli_a920608cfff8dbb6&redirect_uri=http://localhost/oauth/callback&state=calendar\n```\n\n授权完成后，告诉我，我会继续获取 token 并创建测试事件。\n\n（如果授权页面报错，请把错误信息发给我）"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-cn","model":"MiniMax-M2.5","usage":{"input":25882,"output":177,"cacheRead":16705,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":42764,"cost":{"input":0.0077646,"output":0.00021239999999999999,"cacheRead":0.0005011499999999999,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.00847815}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1773124847348}}
{"type":"message","id":"21fdc832","parentId":"f7bd2cef","timestamp":"2026-03-10T06:44:09.248Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Conversation info (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"message_id\": \"om_x100b55cf954eacbcc3e77c2b0e220f2\",\n  \"sender_id\": \"ou_19e8795f6cdecd6c5b87f1545d48b3ca\",\n  \"sender\": \"Roger\",\n  \"timestamp\": \"Tue 2026-03-10 14:44 GMT+8\"\n}\n```\n\nSender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"Roger (ou_19e8795f6cdecd6c5b87f1545d48b3ca)\",\n  \"id\": \"ou_19e8795f6cdecd6c5b87f1545d48b3ca\",\n  \"name\": \"Roger\"\n}\n```\n\n[message_id: om_x100b55cf954eacbcc3e77c2b0e220f2]\nRoger: 我已经授权了，你再想一下有没有什么其他方法"}],"timestamp":1773125049243}}
{"type":"message","id":"32871c36","parentId":"21fdc832","timestamp":"2026-03-10T06:44:19.116Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"用户说已经授权了。通常 OAuth 授权后，会返回一个 code 到 redirect_uri。但这个是 localhost，客户端无法接收。\n\n让我想想其他方案：\n\n1. 飞书支持一种\"批量授权\"的方式，管理员可以在飞书管理后台给应用批量授权某些权限\n2. 或者用户可以直接在日历设置中添加应用为\"可管理\"权限\n\n让我先检查一下当前应用的权限状态，看看有没有 user_access_token 可用。\n\n实际上，更简单的方案是：让用户直接在他的飞书日历设置中，把应用添加为\"可管理\"或\"可编辑\"权限。这样应用就可以用 tenant_access_token 访问了。\n\n让我告诉用户这个更简单的方案。","thinkingSignature":"effb353b97e9b6405f7618fa7308364b105be07767240ad732a5768a57ab60e5"},{"type":"text","text":"\n有一个更简单的方案！**直接在日历设置中添加应用权限**：\n\n---\n\n### 操作步骤\n\n1. 打开飞书日历：https://calendar.feishu.cn/\n\n2. 点击左上角你的日历 → **日历设置**\n\n3. 在\"权限设置\"中：\n   - 添加**应用** (`cli_a920608cfff8dbb6`)\n   - 权限选择：**可编辑** 或 **可管理**\n\n4. 保存\n\n---\n\n这样我就可以用 tenant_access_token 直接操作你的日历了！设置好了告诉我。"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-cn","model":"MiniMax-M2.5","usage":{"input":36,"output":251,"cacheRead":41904,"cacheWrite":978,"totalTokens":43169,"cost":{"input":0.0000108,"output":0.0003012,"cacheRead":0.0012571199999999998,"cacheWrite":0.00011735999999999999,"total":0.0016864799999999998}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1773125049247}}
