9\"\n                  - link [ref=e92] [cursor=pointer]:\n                    - /url: https://github.com/openclaw/skills/tree/main/skills/sunnull/feishu-calendar-tool\n                    - button [ref=e93]:\n                      - img:\n                        - img \"Github\"\n                - generic [ref=e94]:\n                  - generic [ref=e95]: 1.0.1\n                  - img [ref=e96]:\n                    - img [ref=e97]\n                  - link \"openclaw\" [ref=e99] [cursor=pointer]:\n                    - /url: https://github.com/openclaw\n                  - img [ref=e100]:\n                    - img [ref=e101]\n                  - time [ref=e104]: 3月 04, 2026\n            - generic [ref=e105]:\n              - link \"日历日程\" [ref=e106] [cursor=pointer]:\n                - /url: /skills?category=calendar-scheduling\n                - button \"日历日程\" [ref=e107]:\n                  - img [ref=e109]:\n                    - img [ref=e110]\n                  - generic [ref=e112]: 日历日程\n              - generic [ref=e114]:\n                - img [ref=e115]:\n                  - img [ref=e116]\n                - text: 1.9k\n          - generic [ref=e118]:\n            - generic [ref=e119]:\n              - tablist [ref=e121]:\n                - generic [ref=e123]:\n                  - tab \"概览\" [selected] [ref=e125] [cursor=pointer]:\n                    - img [ref=e127]:\n                      - img [ref=e128]\n                    - text: 概览\n                  - tab \"安装方式\" [ref=e131] [cursor=pointer]:\n                    - img [ref=e133]:\n                      - img [ref=e134]\n                    - text: 安装方式\n                  - tab \"SKILL.md\" [ref=e138] [cursor=pointer]:\n                    - img [ref=e140]:\n                      - img [ref=e141]\n                    - text: SKILL.md\n                  - tab \"资源 28\" [ref=e145] [cursor=pointer]:\n                    - img [ref=e147]:\n                      - img [ref=e148]\n                    - generic [ref=e151]:\n                      - text: 资源\n                      - generic [ref=e152]: \"28\"\n                  - tab \"相关 Skills\" [ref=e154] [cursor=pointer]:\n                    - img [ref=e156]:\n                      - img [ref=e157]\n                    - text: 相关 Skills\n                  - tab \"版本历史\" [ref=e159] [cursor=pointer]:\n                    - img [ref=e161]:\n                      - img [ref=e162]\n                    - text: 版本历史\n              - generic [ref=e166]:\n                - link \"需要帮助？\" [ref=e167] [cursor=pointer]:\n                  - /url: https://discord.gg/AYFPHvv2jT\n                - link \"查看源代码\" [ref=e168] [cursor=pointer]:\n                  - /url: https://github.com/openclaw/skills/tree/main/skills/sunnull/feishu-calendar-tool\n                - link \"报告问题\" [ref=e169] [cursor=pointer]:\n                  - /url: https://github.com/openclaw/skills/issues\n            - generic [ref=e170]:\n              - generic [ref=e172]:\n                - generic [ref=e173]:\n                  - heading \"摘要\" [level=2] [ref=e175]\n                  - article [ref=e176]:\n                    - paragraph [ref=e177]: 飞书日历管理工具（feishu-calendar-tool）是一款零配置的命令行日程管理器，自动从 ~/.openclaw/openclaw.json 或环境变量读取飞书凭证并智能缓存 24 小时，自动发现 user_id 与 calendar_id。支持创建、查询、删除日程，包含标题、开始/结束时间、描述、地点、参与人和时区等参数，提供便捷的 CLI 命令用于日常会议排期、批量脚本化调度或 CI 集成。工具按优先级查找凭证并提供测试凭证与查看日历命令，核心优势是快速上手、免运维配置、安全缓存凭证与便于团队日程自动化管理。\n                - generic [ref=e179]:\n                  - generic [ref=e180]:\n                    - button [expanded] [ref=e181] [cursor=pointer]:\n                      - img [ref=e182]:\n                        - img [ref=e183]\n                    - button \"SKILL.md\" [expanded] [ref=e185] [cursor=pointer]:\n                      - generic [ref=e186]: SKILL.md\n                  - article [ref=e190]:\n                    - heading \"飞书日历管理工具 📅\" [level=1] [ref=e191]\n                    - paragraph [ref=e192]:\n                      - text: 简单高效的飞书日历事件管理工具 -\n                      - strong [ref=e193]: 零配置启动！\n                    - heading \"✨ 核心特性\" [level=2] [ref=e194]\n                    - list [ref=e195]:\n                      - listitem [ref=e196]:\n                        - text: \"-\"\n                        - strong [ref=e197]: 零配置\n                        - text: \"- 自动从\"\n                        - code [ref=e198]: ~/.openclaw/openclaw.json\n                        - text: 读取飞书凭证\n                      - listitem [ref=e199]:\n                        - text: \"-\"\n                        - strong [ref=e200]: 自动发现\n                        - text: \"- 自动获取 user_id 和 calendar_id\"\n                      - listitem [ref=e201]:\n                        - text: \"-\"\n                        - strong [ref=e202]: 智能缓存\n                        - text: \"- 凭证和配置缓存 24 小时\"\n                      - listitem [ref=e203]:\n                        - text: \"-\"\n                        - strong [ref=e204]: 创建日程\n                        - text: \"- 支持创建飞书日程事件\"\n                      - listitem [ref=e205]:\n                        - text: \"-\"\n                        - strong [ref=e206]: 删除日程\n                        - text: \"- 支持删除已创建的事件\"\n                      - listitem [ref=e207]:\n                        - text: \"-\"\n                        - strong [ref=e208]: 查询日程\n                        - text: \"- 查看指定日期范围的日程\"\n                    - heading \"快速开始\" [level=2] [ref=e209]\n                    - heading \"零配置使用（推荐）⭐\" [level=3] [ref=e210]\n                    - paragraph [ref=e211]:\n                      - strong [ref=e212]: 已配置飞书通道？无需任何配置，直接使用！\n                    - generic [ref=e213]:\n                      - generic [ref=e214] [cursor=pointer]:\n                        - generic [ref=e215]:\n                          - img \"*.bash\" [ref=e216]\n                          - generic [ref=e217]: Shell\n                        - generic [ref=e218]:\n                          - button [ref=e220]:\n                            - img:\n                              - img\n                          - button [ref=e221]:\n                            - img:\n                              - img\n                      - code [ref=e225]: \"# 创建日程 node bin/create-event.mjs \\\\ --title \\\"团队会议\\\" \\\\ --start \\\"2026-02-10 14:00:00\\\" \\\\ --end \\\"2026-02-10 15:00:00\\\" # 查询日程 node bin/list-events.mjs # 删除日程 node bin/delete-event.mjs --event-id \\\"事件ID\\\"\"\n                    - heading \"首次使用\" [level=3] [ref=e226]\n                    - paragraph [ref=e227]: 如果你还没有配置飞书应用：\n                    - heading \"1. 创建飞书应用\" [level=4] [ref=e228]\n                    - paragraph [ref=e229]:\n                      - text: 访问\n                      - link \"飞书开放平台\" [ref=e230] [cursor=pointer]:\n                        - /url: https://open.feishu.cn/app\n                      - text: 创建应用，获取：\n                    - list [ref=e231]:\n                      - listitem [ref=e232]:\n                        - text: \"-\"\n                        - strong [ref=e233]: App ID\n                      - listitem [ref=e234]:\n                        - text: \"-\"\n                        - strong [ref=e235]: App Secret\n                    - heading \"2. 添加权限\" [level=4] [ref=e236]\n                    - paragraph [ref=e237]: 在应用管理页添加以下权限：\n                    - list [ref=e238]:\n                      - listitem [ref=e239]:\n                        - text: \"- ✅\"\n                        - code [ref=e240]: calendar:calendar\n                        - text: \"- 读写日历\"\n                      - listitem [ref=e241]:\n                        - text: \"- ✅\"\n                        - code [ref=e242]: calendar:calendar:readonly\n                        - text: \"- 读取日历\"\n                      - listitem [ref=e243]:\n                        - text: \"- ✅\"\n                        - code [ref=e244]: contact:user.base:readonly\n                        - text: \"- 自动获取 user_id\"\n                      - listitem [ref=e245]:\n                        - text: \"- ✅\"\n                        - code [ref=e246]: contact:user.employee_id:readonly\n                        - text: \"- 读取员工目录\"\n                    - heading \"3. 配置到 openclaw.json\" [level=4] [ref=e247]\n                    - paragraph [ref=e248]:\n                      - text: 编辑\n                      - code [ref=e249]: ~/.openclaw/openclaw.json\n                      - text: ：\n                    - generic [ref=e250]:\n                      - generic [ref=e251] [cursor=pointer]:\n                        - generic [ref=e252]:\n                          - img \"*.json\" [ref=e253]\n                          - generic [ref=e254]: JSON\n                        - generic [ref=e255]:\n                          - button [ref=e257]:\n                            - img:\n                              - img\n                          - button [ref=e258]:\n                            - img:\n                              - img\n                      - code [ref=e262]: \"{ \\\"channels\\\": { \\\"feishu\\\": { \\\"accounts\\\": { \\\"default\\\": { \\\"appId\\\": \\\"你的AppID\\\", \\\"appSecret\\\": \\\"你的AppSecret\\\", \\\"enabled\\\": true } } } } }\"\n                    - paragraph [ref=e263]:\n                      - strong [ref=e264]: 完成！现在可以零配置使用了。\n                    - heading \"使用方法\" [level=2] [ref=e265]\n                    - heading \"创建日程\" [level=3] [ref=e266]\n                    - generic [ref=e267]:\n                      - generic [ref=e268] [cursor=pointer]:\n                        - generic [ref=e269]:\n                          - img \"*.bash\" [ref=e270]\n                          - generic [ref=e271]: Shell\n                        - generic [ref=e272]:\n                          - button [ref=e274]:\n                            - img:\n                              - img\n                          - button [ref=e275]:\n                            - img:\n                              - img\n                      - code [ref=e279]: node bin/create-event.mjs \\ --title \"周会议\" \\ --start \"2026-02-10 17:00:00\" \\ --end \"2026-02-10 18:00:00\" \\ --description \"每周例会\" \\ --location \"会议室A\"\n                    - paragraph [ref=e280]:\n                      - strong [ref=e281]: 参数说明：\n                    - list [ref=e282]:\n                      - listitem [ref=e283]:\n                        - text: \"-\"\n                        - code [ref=e284]: \"--title\"\n                        - text: \"- 日程标题（必需）\"\n                      - listitem [ref=e285]:\n                        - text: \"-\"\n                        - code [ref=e286]: \"--start\"\n                        - text: \"- 开始时间，格式：YYYY-MM-DD HH:MM:SS（必需）\"\n                      - listitem [ref=e287]:\n                        - text: \"-\"\n                        - code [ref=e288]: \"--end\"\n                        - text: \"- 结束时间，格式：YYYY-MM-DD HH:MM:SS（必需）\"\n                      - listitem [ref=e289]:\n                        - text: \"-\"\n                        - code [ref=e290]: \"--description\"\n                        - text: \"- 日程描述（可选）\"\n                      - listitem [ref=e291]:\n                        - text: \"-\"\n                        - code [ref=e292]: \"--location\"\n                        - text: \"- 地点（可选）\"\n                      - listitem [ref=e293]:\n                        - text: \"-\"\n                        - code [ref=e294]: \"--attendees\"\n                        - text: \"- 参与人，逗号分隔（可选）\"\n                      - listitem [ref=e295]:\n                        - text: \"-\"\n                        - code [ref=e296]: \"--timezone\"\n                        - text: \"- 时区，默认 Asia/Shanghai（可选）\"\n                    - heading \"查询日程\" [level=3] [ref=e297]\n                    - generic [ref=e298]:\n                      - generic [ref=e299] [cursor=pointer]:\n                        - generic [ref=e300]:\n                          - img \"*.bash\" [ref=e301]\n                          - generic [ref=e302]: Shell\n                        - generic [ref=e303]:\n                          - button [ref=e305]:\n                            - img:\n                              - img\n                          - button [ref=e306]:\n                            - img:\n                              - img\n                      - code [ref=e310]: \"# 查看未来 7 天的日程 node bin/list-events.mjs # 查看指定日期范围 node bin/list-events.mjs \\\\ --start \\\"2026-02-10\\\" \\\\ --end \\\"2026-02-17\\\"\"\n                    - heading \"删除日程\" [level=3] [ref=e311]\n                    - generic [ref=e312]:\n                      - generic [ref=e313] [cursor=pointer]:\n                        - generic [ref=e314]:\n                          - img \"*.bash\" [ref=e315]\n                          - generic [ref=e316]: Shell\n                        - generic [ref=e317]:\n                          - button [ref=e319]:\n                            - img:\n                              - img\n                          - button [ref=e320]:\n                            - img:\n                              - img\n                      - code [ref=e324]: node bin/delete-event.mjs --event-id \"事件ID\"\n                    - heading \"配置方式\" [level=2] [ref=e325]\n                    - heading \"自动查找顺序\" [level=3] [ref=e326]\n                    - list [ref=e327]:\n                      - listitem [ref=e328]:\n                        - strong [ref=e329]: 环境变量\n                        - text: \"- 如果已设置\"\n                      - listitem [ref=e330]:\n                        - strong [ref=e331]: ~/.openclaw/openclaw.json\n                        - text: \"- 推荐 ⭐\"\n                      - listitem [ref=e332]:\n                        - strong [ref=e333]: ~/openclaw/.secrets.env\n                      - listitem [ref=e334]:\n                        - strong [ref=e335]: ~/.secrets.env\n                    - heading \"验证配置\" [level=2] [ref=e336]\n                    - generic [ref=e337]:\n                      - generic [ref=e338] [cursor=pointer]:\n                        - generic [ref=e339]:\n                          - img \"*.bash\" [ref=e340]\n                          - generic [ref=e341]: Shell\n                        - generic [ref=e342]:\n                          - button [ref=e344]:\n                            - img:\n                              - img\n                          - button [ref=e345]:\n                            - img:\n                              - img\n                      - code [ref=e349]: \"# 测试凭证加载 node bin/test-credentials.mjs # 查看可用的日历 node bin/get-user-info.mjs\"\n                    - paragraph [ref=e350]: 成功输出：\n                    - generic [ref=e351]:\n                      - generic [ref=e352] [cursor=pointer]:\n                        - generic [ref=e353]:\n                          - img \"*.txt\" [ref=e354]\n                          - generic [ref=e355]: Plaintext\n                        - generic [ref=e356]:\n                          - button [ref=e358]:\n                            - img:\n                              - img\n                          - button [ref=e359]:\n                            - img:\n                              - img\n                      - code [ref=e363]: \"✅ Credentials loaded successfully! Source: /home/user/.openclaw/openclaw.json App ID: cli_xxxxxxxxxxxxx\"\n                    - heading \"自动发现功能\" [level=2] [ref=e364]\n                    - list [ref=e365]:\n                      - listitem [ref=e366]:\n                        - text: \"-\"\n                        - strong [ref=e367]: user_id\n                        - text: \"- 通过飞书 API 自动获取当前用户 ID\"\n                      - listitem [ref=e368]:\n                        - text: \"-\"\n                        - strong [ref=e369]: calendar_id\n                        - text: \"- 自动选择主日历（primary calendar）\"\n                      - listitem [ref=e370]:\n                        - text: \"-\"\n                        - strong [ref=e371]: 缓存\n                        - text: \"- 结果缓存 24 小时，减少 API 调用\"\n                    - heading \"技术实现\" [level=2] [ref=e372]\n                    - list [ref=e373]:\n                      - listitem [ref=e374]: \"- 使用飞书 Calendar v4 API\"\n                      - listitem [ref=e375]: \"- 自动处理 access token 获取和刷新\"\n                      - listitem [ref=e376]: \"- 智能错误重试机制\"\n                      - listitem [ref=e377]: \"- 支持 Asia/Shanghai 时区\"\n                    - heading \"常见问题\" [level=2] [ref=e378]\n                    - 'heading \"Q: 我已经配置了飞书通道，还需要重新配置吗？\" [level=3] [ref=e379]'\n                    - paragraph [ref=e380]:\n                      - text: \"A:\"\n                      - strong [ref=e381]: 不需要！\n                      - text: 技能会自动读取\n                      - code [ref=e382]: openclaw.json\n                      - text: 中的凭证，直接使用即可。\n                    - 'heading \"Q: 支持多个飞书账户吗？\" [level=3] [ref=e383]'\n                    - paragraph [ref=e384]:\n                      - text: \"A: 支持！在\"\n                      - code [ref=e385]: openclaw.json\n                      - text: 中配置多个账户，技能会优先使用\n                      - code [ref=e386]: default\n                      - text: 账户。\n                    - 'heading \"Q: 如何查看我的日历 ID？\" [level=3] [ref=e387]'\n                    - paragraph [ref=e388]:\n                      - text: \"A: 运行\"\n                      - code [ref=e389]: node bin/get-user-info.mjs\n                      - text: 查看所有可用的日历。\n                    - 'heading \"Q: 技能会修改我的 openclaw.json 吗？\" [level=3] [ref=e390]'\n                    - paragraph [ref=e391]:\n                      - text: \"A:\"\n                      - strong [ref=e392]: 不会！\n                      - text: 技能只读取配置，从不修改。\n                    - heading \"相关链接\" [level=2] [ref=e393]\n                    - list [ref=e394]:\n                      - listitem [ref=e395]:\n                        - text: \