{"type":"message","id":"c93b0c63","parentId":"ed53d4f8","timestamp":"2026-03-10T11:28:21.001Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"我找到了一个现成的飞书日历技能！叫做 `feishu-calendar-tool`，看起来非常适合 Roger 的需求。它有以下特点：\n\n1. 零配置 - 自动从 `~/.openclaw/openclaw.json` 读取飞书凭证\n2. 自动发现 user_id 和 calendar_id\n3. 支持创建、查询、删除日程\n\n关键的是，这个技能告诉我：\n- 如果已经配置了飞书通道，不需要重新配置，技能会自动读取 `openclaw.json` 中的凭证\n\n我应该告诉 Roger 这个好消息！并告诉他如何安装这个技能。","thinkingSignature":"a5e1bb930204d1b0d6b276469653103f73198151c052f50998055ec4d79b625d"},{"type":"text","text":"太棒了！找到了一个现成的解决方案！\n\n---\n\n## 飞书日历技能 (feishu-calendar-tool)\n\n这个技能正好满足你的需求：\n- ✅ **零配置** - 自动读取飞书凭证\n- ✅ **自动发现** - 自动获取 user_id 和 calendar_id\n- ✅ **创建/查询/删除** - 日历管理功能完整\n\n---\n\n### 安装步骤\n\n你需要把这个技能安装到你的 OpenClaw。让我帮你安装：\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_lix6eki1x7y0_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"cd C:\\Users\\73911\\.openclaw && git clone https://github.com/lobehub/skill-feishu-calendar-tool.git skills/feishu-calendar-tool 2>&1 || curl -L https://github.com/lobehub/skill-feishu-calendar-tool/archive/main.zip -o temp.zip 2>&1"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-cn","model":"MiniMax-M2.5","usage":{"input":48255,"output":305,"cacheRead":16705,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":65265,"cost":{"input":0.0144765,"output":0.000366,"cacheRead":0.0005011499999999999,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.01534365}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1773142089156}}
