{"type":"message","id":"f2fbb4ed","parentId":"18113ea9","timestamp":"2026-03-10T11:52:06.226Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Hmm, there's an error getting the access token. This is likely because the app ID is incorrect for this skill - this skill expects a different app. Let me try to check what the actual issue is. \n\nActually wait, let me try updating the skill to use the correct app. The error \"invalid param\" might be because the app credentials aren't correct. Let me try manually calling the API to get the access token.\n\nActually, this skill is probably expecting the lark suite endpoint (for international lark) not feishu.cn. Let me check the code.","thinkingSignature":"3e10f919b32c469bd292902150a27a91a668430f9613fb627090846011d13630"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_9smah212psgo_1","name":"read","arguments":{"path":"C:\\Users\\73911\\.openclaw\\skills\\openclaw-skills-lark-calendar\\lib\\lark-api.mjs","limit":50}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-cn","model":"MiniMax-M2.5","usage":{"input":66925,"output":176,"cacheRead":16810,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":83911,"cost":{"input":0.020077499999999998,"output":0.00021119999999999998,"cacheRead":0.0005043,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.020793}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1773143520673}}
{"type":"message","id":"3b51b427","parentId":"f2fbb4ed","timestamp":"2026-03-10T11:52:06.255Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_9smah212psgo_1","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"/**\n * Lark (Feishu) API Wrapper\n * Handles authentication and API calls with automatic token refresh\n */\n\nimport { config } from 'dotenv';\nimport { fileURLToPath } from 'url';\nimport { dirname, join } from 'path';\n\n// Load secrets\nconst __dirname = dirname(fileURLToPath(import.meta.url));\nconfig({ path: join(__dirname, '../../../../.secrets.env') });\n\nconst APP_ID = process.env.FEISHU_APP_ID;\nconst APP_SECRET = process.env.FEISHU_APP_SECRET;\n\n// Use larksuite.com for international Lark\nconst BASE_URL = 'https://open.larksuite.com/open-apis';\n\nlet accessToken = null;\nlet tokenExpiry = 0;\n\n/**\n * Get or refresh access token\n */\nasync function getAccessToken() {\n  // Return cached token if still valid (with 5 min buffer)\n  if (accessToken && Date.now() < tokenExpiry - 300000) {\n    return accessToken;\n  }\n  \n  const response = await fetch(`${BASE_URL}/auth/v3/tenant_access_token/internal`, {\n    method: 'POST',\n    headers: { 'Content-Type': 'application/json' },\n    body: JSON.stringify({\n      app_id: APP_ID,\n      app_secret: APP_SECRET\n    })\n  });\n  \n  const data = await response.json();\n  \n  if (data.code !== 0) {\n    throw new Error(`Failed to get access token: ${JSON.stringify(data)}`);\n  }\n  \n  accessToken = `Bearer ${data.tenant_access_token}`;\n  // Token expires in ~2 hours, we store expiry time\n  tokenExpiry = Date.now() + (data.expire * 1000);\n  \n\n[87 more lines in file. Use offset=51 to continue.]"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1773143526247}}
{"type":"message","id":"6ce527f0","parentId":"3b51b427","timestamp":"2026-03-10T11:52:39.188Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Ah I see! This skill is using `open.larksuite.com` (international Lark) not `open.feishu.cn` (China Feishu). That's why it's failing. The credentials Roger provided are for feishu.cn (China), not larksuite.com (international).\n\nLet me check if there's a way to configure this skill to use the China endpoint instead. Or I could try a different approach - using the earlier feishu-calendar-tool skill but fixing its issues.\n\nActually, let me go back to our earlier solution - we had already created a Bitable calendar which works fine. The user can view events there. That was the simplest solution.\n\nLet me update the user on the current status and suggest we go back to the Bitable solution since it works reliably.","thinkingSignature":"f2637f7e72fe547f0c2ed9509596b8cf8bfaa50f75575f5a92d92acf828694f7"},{"type":"text","text":"我发现问题了 — 这个技能使用的是 **国际版 Lark (larksuite.com)**，而你的是 **中国飞书 (feishu.cn)**。\n\n---\n\n**当前状况总结：**\n\n| 方案 | 状态 |\n|------|------|\n| 飞书日历 API | ❌ 需要复杂的用户授权 |\n| feishu-calendar-tool 技能 | ❌ 代码兼容性问题 |\n| lark-calendar 技能 | ❌ 用于国际版，不适用 |\n| **Bitable 表格** | ✅ 已可用 |\n\n---\n\n**推荐方案：** 回到我们之前创建的 **Bitable 日历表格**，它已经可以正常使用了！\n\n**日历地址：** https://xoyl7kym2j.feishu.cn/base/DXMNb7sbVaHea2suU4FcITuMnig\n\n你可以直接在里面创建/查看/修改事件，我也可以帮你管理。\n\n要不要先用 Bitable 方案？如果之后需要真正的日历 API，我们可以再研究。"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-cn","model":"MiniMax-M2.5","usage":{"input":67486,"output":361,"cacheRead":16810,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":84657,"cost":{"input":0.020245799999999998,"output":0.00043319999999999996,"cacheRead":0.0005043,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.0211833}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1773143526257}}
