{"type":"message","id":"064e7ead","parentId":"5a12454c","timestamp":"2026-03-10T11:53:54.146Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"搜索结果提到了OpenClaw的飞书集成，包括需要配置哪些日历权限。让我看看搜索结果中提到了一个CSDN文章，提到了需要的权限：\n\n```\n\"calendar:calendar.event:create\", \"calendar:calendar.event:delete\", \"calendar:calendar.event:read\", \"calendar:calendar.event:reply\", \"calendar:calendar.event:update\", \"calendar:calendar.free_busy:read\"\n```\n\n这正是我们之前尝试使用的权限。但问题是我们使用的是 tenant_access_token，它无法直接访问用户的个人日历。让我看看能否找到一个更详细的教程。","thinkingSignature":"ddc7d588df61a62de3e879133528439b42f4634a4d866de28767475493ac8fd9"},{"type":"text","text":"我找到了一些有用的信息！搜索结果显示需要配置特定的日历权限。让我查看其中一个详细的教程：\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_skj0nv3i1oov_1","name":"browser","arguments":{"action":"navigate","targetId":"170B3265461B2AE3B490B530C5B3D70D","url":"https://ligh60.blog.csdn.net/article/details/136130268"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-cn","model":"MiniMax-M2.5","usage":{"input":87499,"output":216,"cacheRead":16810,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":104525,"cost":{"input":0.026249699999999997,"output":0.0002592,"cacheRead":0.0005043,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.027013199999999998}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1773143611474}}
