87]:\n            - link \"版权与免责声明\" [ref=e288] [cursor=pointer]:\n              - /url: https://www.csdn.net/company/index.html#statement\n          - listitem [ref=e289]:\n            - link \"版权申诉\" [ref=e290] [cursor=pointer]:\n              - /url: https://blog.csdn.net/blogdevteam/article/details/90369522\n          - listitem [ref=e291]:\n            - link \"出版物许可证\" [ref=e292] [cursor=pointer]:\n              - /url: https://img-home.csdnimg.cn/images/20250103023206.png\n          - listitem [ref=e293]:\n            - link \"营业执照\" [ref=e294] [cursor=pointer]:\n              - /url: https://img-home.csdnimg.cn/images/20250103023201.png\n          - listitem [ref=e295]: ©1999-2026北京创新乐知网络技术有限公司\n<<<END_EXTERNAL_UNTRUSTED_CONTENT id=\"f89d15a0f982349a\">>>"}],"details":{"ok":true,"format":"ai","targetId":"170B3265461B2AE3B490B530C5B3D70D","url":"https://ligh60.blog.csdn.net/article/details/136130268","refs":232,"externalContent":{"untrusted":true,"source":"browser","kind":"snapshot","format":"ai","wrapped":true}},"isError":false,"timestamp":1773143639309}}
{"type":"message","id":"9aa0ae4a","parentId":"0f76c865","timestamp":"2026-03-10T11:54:15.720Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"这个CSDN文章已经被删除了。让我看看其他搜索结果，找一个更有用的链接。我注意到在之前的百度搜索结果中，有一篇文章提到了具体的权限配置：\n- \"calendar:calendar.event:create\", \"calendar:calendar.event:delete\", \"calendar:calendar.event:read\", \"calendar:calendar.event:reply\", \"calendar:calendar.event:update\", \"calendar:calendar.free_busy:read\"\n\n问题是飞书API需要用户授权才能访问个人日历，tenant_access_token不够。让我总结一下当前情况和下一步建议。","thinkingSignature":"654d4efa919d6d6118d56a958043bbdbcbfed28fb2f15fff077c234717755c5f"},{"type":"text","text":"搜索结果有用的信息不多。根据我的研究，总结一下当前情况：\n\n---\n\n## 总结：OpenClaw 在飞书日历创建事件的方案\n\n### 问题根源\n飞书日历 API 需要 **用户授权 (user_access_token)** 才能访问个人日历，单纯使用应用凭证 (tenant_access_token) 无法直接操作用户日历。\n\n### 现有方案\n\n| 方案 | 状态 | 说明 |\n|------|------|------|\n| **Bitable 表格** | ✅ 可用 | 已创建，可以正常创建/查看/修改事件 |\n| 飞书日历 API | ❌ 复杂 | 需要 OAuth 用户授权流程 |\n| 现有技能 | ❌ 兼容性问题 | 代码有bug或仅支持国际版 |\n\n### 推荐：Bitable 方案\n\n你已经有一个可用的日历表格：\n- **地址**：https://xoyl7kym2j.feishu.cn/base/DXMNb7sbVaHea2suU4FcITuMnig\n- 功能：创建、查看、修改事件\n\n我可以直接帮你管理这个日历，比如：\n- \"帮我创建日历：项目评审会，明天上午10点\"\n\n---\n\n你想要先用 Bitable 方案，还是想深入研究飞书日历 API 的用户授权配置？"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-cn","model":"MiniMax-M2.5","usage":{"input":99095,"output":365,"cacheRead":16810,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":116270,"cost":{"input":0.029728499999999998,"output":0.00043799999999999997,"cacheRead":0.0005043,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.030670799999999998}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1773143639317}}
