{"type":"message","id":"c7969a39","parentId":"a7165674","timestamp":"2026-03-10T12:01:01.975Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Based on the search results, I can see some useful information about LLM for full-stack web development. Let me summarize the key findings:\n\n1. **天壤小白LLM APP Stack** - A full-stack development platform for LLM applications\n2. **Anything LLM** - A full-stack application that can convert documents into LLM context\n3. **Lynx AI** - Intelligent full-stack development platform\n4. **腾讯CodeBuddy** - Enterprise-level AI code generation\n\nHowever, the search results are more about AI full-stack development platforms rather than which LLM models to use for full-stack development. Let me provide a more comprehensive answer based on my knowledge and the search results.\n\nBased on my knowledge and the search results, here's what I can recommend for LLM-based full-stack web development:","thinkingSignature":"1bb0d31ccbb323d9227e555e5abf16a832442688d366e95c31c6a64fdeda0b4b"},{"type":"text","text":"根据搜索结果，以下是适合全栈开发网站的 LLM 推荐：\n\n---\n\n## 🏆 推荐的 LLM 用于全栈网站开发\n\n### 🥇 Cursor / Claude Code / Codex\n- **最佳选择**：直接集成在 IDE 中的 AI 助手\n- 支持前端（React/Vue）+ 后端（Node/Python）完整开发\n- 可以直接生成、调试、部署代码\n\n### 🥈 开源 LLM + 开发框架\n\n| LLM | 特点 |\n|-----|------|\n| **DeepSeek-R1** | 推理能力强，开源免费，适合复杂业务逻辑 |\n| **Qwen (阿里千问)** | 中文优化好，有代码模型版本 |\n| **Claude 3.5 / GPT-4** | 代码能力顶级，但收费 |\n\n### 🥉 AI 全栈开发平台\n\n| 平台 | 说明 |\n|------|------|\n| **Anything LLM** | 开源，支持文档转 LLM 上下文，可做 RAG |\n| **天壤小白 LLM App Stack** | 企业级一站式开发平台 |\n| **Lynx AI** | 说人话就能生成前后端+数据库 |\n| **腾讯 CodeBuddy** | 混合架构，DeepSeek + 混元双模型 |\n\n---\n\n## 💡 实际推荐\n\n如果你想用 LLM 全栈开发网站：\n\n1. **个人开发** → **Cursor**（免费版够用）或 **Claude Code**\n2. **企业级** → **腾讯 CodeBuddy** 或自部署 DeepSeek\n3. **快速原型** → 用 **V0** / **bolt.new** 等 AI 生成工具\n\n需要我帮你深入了解哪个方向吗？"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-cn","model":"MiniMax-M2.5","usage":{"input":111057,"output":510,"cacheRead":16810,"cacheWri