{"type":"message","id":"0511bec0","parentId":"09fb145c","timestamp":"2026-03-10T12:02:45.478Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Let me try another approach - I'll use my knowledge to answer this question without searching.","thinkingSignature":"f2d420fb340c458d814ee903a8964fad72c0b84c481e7ee272006397a40498b4"},{"type":"text","text":"好的，不用百度。根据我的了解，直接给你推荐：\n\n---\n\n## 推荐 LLM 全栈开发网站\n\n### 🏆 最佳选择\n\n| LLM | 适用场景 | 价格 |\n|-----|---------|------|\n| **Cursor** | IDE 集成，直接写代码+调试+部署 | 免费/付费 |\n| **Claude Code** | 专业代码开发，React/Vue/Node 都很强 | 免费 |\n| **Codex (OpenAI)** | CLI 工具，VS Code/Claude Code 底层 | 免费 |\n\n### 🔧 开源自部署\n\n| LLM | 特点 |\n|-----|------|\n| **DeepSeek Coder V2** | 开源免费，代码能力接近 GPT-4 |\n| **Qwen2.5-Coder** | 阿里开源，中文友好 |\n| **CodeLlama** | Meta 开源，可本地运行 |\n\n### 🛠️ AI 生成网站工具\n\n| 工具 | 说明 |\n|------|------|\n| **v0 (Vercel)** | 描述需求 → 生成 React 网站 |\n| **bolt.new** | AI 全栈生成 + 部署 |\n| **Loops** | AI 网站构建器 |\n\n---\n\n**推荐组合**：**Cursor + DeepSeek** 或 **v0 + Claude**，基本可以搞定全栈网站开发。\n\n需要我帮你配置哪个？"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-cn","model":"MiniMax-M2.5","usage":{"input":111705,"output":297,"cacheRead":16810,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":128812,"cost":{"input":0.0335115,"output":0.0003564,"cacheRead":0.0005043,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.0343722}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1773144147516}}
